<h2>Bhedadƒ´pikƒÅ - An Illustration of Duality</h2>
<p>
	The concept of Duality has intrigued mankind since the beginning of civilization. This work in collaboration with ESA ILEWG Moon Gallery Project, plays upon several notions of Duality such as:
	<ul>
		<li>Constraint/Freedom</li>
		<li>Light/Darkness</li>
		<li>Minute/Infinite</li>
		<li>Reality/Illusion</li>
		<li>Randomness/Intent</li>
	</ul>			
</p>
<p>
	The artwork comprises of two objects constrained inside a 1cm¬≥ box: a strip of paper, and a nano-sim card. 
	<br /><br />
	For more information on the Moon Gallery Project, check out my <a href="/Space/MoonGallery"> page here</a>, or go to the official <a href="http://www.moongallery.eu/">Moon Gallery</a> website.
</p>

